<h3>Icons</h3>

<p>
    Icons can be used within Breadcrumb labels.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Icons should be on the left side of the text label.</li>
    <li>Icons should not be used as the only content of the label.</li>
    <li>If an icon is represented on any single label in the Breadcrumb trail, then icons should be used for all labels in the Breadcrumb trail.</li>
</ul>

